{"type": "article", "id": 9452, "title": "豆腐制作器", "description": "", "date": "2015-05-12T07:10:33Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 8, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605235340tATqdbzVfyEvG3ml.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t这是一套专门用来制作中式传统豆腐的容器，其中包括碗，编织笼等等，从烹饪，压制，切割，食用全方位服务豆腐的制作和食用，纯天然的材料保持豆腐的新鲜和养分。值得一提的是，这件作品是王未未（音译）在包豪斯学院的本科毕业作品，并在米兰家具展期间进行了展出，这是<a href=\"http://www.weiwei-wang.com/\" target=\"_blank\">设计师的个人主页</a>，感兴趣的话，可以查看她更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;min-height:13px;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235338j7sxaBW3zDZJCf2i.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235338ufaTpjIQAgmPZWHG.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235338aQNBOg9qpZ5UDzIo.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606052353391KJ36Fu7c9UMhP4q.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605235339oXkKAmv6ep2Ncfnj.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;\" data-ratio=\"0.71428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;white-space:normal;margin-bottom:16px !important;\">\r\n\t<br>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}